text: Michał Chodara (born 17 March 1986) is a Polish handball player for SPR Stal Mielec and the Polish national team.Michał Chodara He participated at the 2013 World Men's Handball Championship. ==References== Category:1986 births Category:Living people Category:People from Biłgoraj Category:Polish male handball players Category:Vive Kielce players
